# Project1_Blackjack
Blackjack game

For this project I used a combination HTML, CSS, Javascript and jQuery.

Theres's a bug where it doesn't pay out if you get Blackjack. Also, there needs to be a condition for what happens if the player or dealer's bank goes below 0.
